<p>The original distribution supports the following fourteen languages:</p>

<pre class="sh_perl">            1   ==&#62;   English                     (default)
            2   ==&#62;   Fran&#231;ais    (French)
            3   ==&#62;   Deutsch     (German)
            4   ==&#62;   Espa&#241;ol     (Spanish)
